items.title: The Home Depot grows its flatbed distribution network
items.description: The company has three FDCs under construction with more in the pipeline, Senior EVP Ann-Marie Campbell said during its earnings call.

items.title: NAIL: Not All Doom And Gloom For Homebuilders Even If Recession Strikes
items.description: NAIL ETF seeks to deliver 300% (3x) of the return of U.S. stocks exposed to the home construction sector. Read why I remain bullish on the fund.
